title: Cameron 7: The Finale by Jade Jones.epub
description:
Cam, Jude, and Jag are back in the riveting, final installment of the "Cameron" series. What started out as a new beginning soon turns sour after the love of her life becomes her worst enemy. They say 'the grass is never greener on the other side' and now Cameron finally realizes that...but is it too late? Will Jude be able to right his wrongs in time to save his wife? After all, he's part of the reason she landed herself in the situation she's in. Haunted by his past actions, Jude gets a crash course--eventually,in due time, you reap what you sow.
In this dangerous game of love, who will come out the victor and who'll be left broken-hearted?
